import React from "react"
import FirstComp from "./First"
import WithParams from "./WithParams"
import FragmentComp from "./FragmentComp"
import RandNum from "./RandNum"
import Card from "./../layout/Card"

export default () => {
    return (
        //short way to use Fragment
        <>
            <Card>
                <Family familyName="Alves"></Family>
            </Card>
            <Card title="Número aleatório" bgColor="#800">
                <RandNum min={1} max={10} />
            </Card>
            <Card title="Fragmento" bgColor="#080">
                <FragmentComp />
            </Card>
            <Card title="Com parâmetros" bgColor="#008">
                <WithParams title="Lorem ipsum" subtitle="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit" />
            </Card>
            <Card title="Primeiro componente" bgColor="#880">
                <FirstComp />
            </Card>
        </>
    )
}
